<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:08:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>检察官在封口费审判中称特朗普密谋破坏2016年大选</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-schemed-to-corrupt-2016-election-prosecutor-says-in-hush-money-trial/articleshow/109509727.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109509727.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普因策划一项犯罪计划而面临审判，该计划通过向包括一名色情明星在内的女性支付封口费来影响 2016 年大选。审判结果可能会影响他与乔·拜登即将举行的选举复赛的候选资格。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 17:27:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-schemed-to-corrupt-2016-election-prosecutor-says-in-hush-money-trial/articleshow/109509727.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普接受纽约民事欺诈案中 1.75 亿美元保释金的新限制</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-accepts-new-restrictions-on-175-million-bond-in-new-york-civil-fraud-case/articleshow/109508971.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109508971.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;前总统唐纳德·特朗普同意对纽约民事欺诈案中的 1.75 亿美元债券实施更严格的限制，旨在解决对资金安全的担忧。该协议涉及对抵押品和月度报表条款的独家控制。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 16:24:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-accepts-new-restrictions-on-175-million-bond-in-new-york-civil-fraud-case/articleshow/109508971.cms</guid></item><item><title>BBC顶级新闻主播因性爱照片风波而辞职</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/top-bbc-news-anchor-resigns-after-sex-photos-furore/articleshow/109506737.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109506737.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;该广播公司表示，资深新闻主播休·爱德华兹 (Huw Edwards) 因“医疗建议”于周一从 BBC 辞职，九个月前，他卷入了涉及青少年的露骨色情图片丑闻。今年早些时候，BBC 向一名男子的家人道歉，广播公司称爱德华兹在青少年时期曾为该男子付费购买色情图片。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/top-bbc-news-anchor-resigns-after-sex-photos-furore/articleshow/109506737.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国秘书长接受近东救济工程处的独立审查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-chief-accepts-independent-review-of-unrwa/articleshow/109505536.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109505536.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 13:02:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-chief-accepts-independent-review-of-unrwa/articleshow/109505536.cms</guid></item><item><title>耶鲁大学犹太学生在反以色列抗议报道中被巴勒斯坦国旗刺伤眼睛</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/jewish-yale-student-stabbed-in-eye-with-palestine-flag-during-anti-israel-protest-reporting/articleshow/109502848.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109502848.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;耶鲁大学犹太学生记者萨哈尔·塔塔克在报道反以色列抗议活动时遭到袭击。她的眼睛被巴勒斯坦国旗刺伤，并面临示威者的恐吓。尽管她向校园警察报告了这一事件，但她被告知他们无法干预。停止反犹太主义寻求公众帮助来识别袭击者。耶鲁大学官员谴责了暴力事件，但一些人批评该大学没有执行抗议准则。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:41:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/jewish-yale-student-stabbed-in-eye-with-palestine-flag-during-anti-israel-protest-reporting/articleshow/109502848.cms</guid></item><item><title>“中国是马尔代夫议会选举的赢家”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/maldivian-president-muizzus-pro-china-party-secures-super-majority-in-parliamentary-polls/articleshow/109501683.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109501683.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;马尔代夫总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖庆祝议会选举取得重大胜利，赢得人民全国代表大会 (PNC) 93 个席位中的 67 个席位。这次压倒性的胜利不仅为他的政党提供了三分之二的绝对多数，而且还获得了五位联盟立法者的支持。预计这种权力转移将推进许多由北京资助和中国建造的项目。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:01:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/maldivian-president-muizzus-pro-china-party-secures-super-majority-in-parliamentary-polls/articleshow/109501683.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着无家可归者人数的增加，最高法院将考虑禁止户外睡觉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/with-homelessness-on-the-rise-supreme-court-to-weigh-bans-on-sleeping-outdoors/articleshow/109490310.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109490310.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最高法院将决定禁止无家可归者在外面睡觉是否残忍。美国无家可归危机创历史新高。 CA认为这是违宪的。官员、倡导者、司法部都参与其中。格兰茨帕斯对无家可归者处以罚款。第九巡回法院的裁决受到质疑。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 05:11:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/with-homelessness-on-the-rise-supreme-court-to-weigh-bans-on-sleeping-outdoors/articleshow/109490310.cms</guid></item><item><title>梅拉尼娅如何在唐纳德·特朗普的刑事审判中提供帮助</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/how-melania-could-help-donald-trumps-in-his-criminal-trial/articleshow/109501534.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109501534.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;梅拉尼娅·特朗普可能会在纽约审判中加强唐纳德·特朗普的辩护。斯托米·丹尼尔斯的封口费是核心。梅拉尼娅的潜在证词意味着支持，影响陪审团的看法。审判强调书面证据而不是耸人听闻。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:46:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/how-melania-could-help-donald-trumps-in-his-criminal-trial/articleshow/109501534.cms</guid></item><item><title>“永远的战争”：埃隆·马斯克对乌克兰“不退出战略”表示担忧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/forever-war-elon-musk-voices-concern-over-no-exit-strategy-in-ukraine/articleshow/109499893.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109499893.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;埃隆·马斯克批评乌克兰援助缺乏问责制，向基辅提供星链服务，拒绝在塞瓦斯托波尔附近提供服务。美国众议院批准援助，泽连斯基表示感谢，克里姆林宫警告不要一揽子计划。马斯克敦促在冲突中解决问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:03:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/forever-war-elon-musk-voices-concern-over-no-exit-strategy-in-ukraine/articleshow/109499893.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国首相苏纳克承诺，第一批驱逐航班将在 10 至 12 周内离开英国飞往卢旺达</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-prime-minister-rishi-sunak-pushes-for-rwanda-deportation-bill-over-objections-from-unelected-upper-chamber/articleshow/109500101.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109500101.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 承诺，该国第一批驱逐航班可能会在 10 至 12 周内起飞，并承诺结束议会在该措施上的僵局。苏纳克在周一上午的新闻发布会上发表了上述言论，在上周誓言议会将继续开会直至立法获得通过后，他直接向公众阐述了自己的观点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-prime-minister-rishi-sunak-pushes-for-rwanda-deportation-bill-over-objections-from-unelected-upper-chamber/articleshow/109500101.cms</guid></item><item><title>从阿波罗到阿尔忒弥斯：为什么将人类送上月球如此困难</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/from-apollo-to-artemis-why-its-so-difficult-to-send-humans-to-moon/articleshow/109500019.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109500019.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于预算限制、政治意愿减弱、基础设施决策、复杂的目标以及持久的月球遗产愿景，美国宇航局的阿尔忒弥斯计划面临挑战。克服这些障碍对于美国宇航局的现代太空探索工作至关重要。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:58:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/from-apollo-to-artemis-why-its-so-difficult-to-send-humans-to-moon/articleshow/109500019.cms</guid></item><item><title>“反犹太主义，危险”：白宫就哥伦比亚大学的抗议活动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/antisemitic-dangerous-white-house-on-protests-at-columbia-university/articleshow/109499714.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109499714.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:58:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/antisemitic-dangerous-white-house-on-protests-at-columbia-university/articleshow/109499714.cms</guid></item><item><title>国际劳工组织表示，随着气候变化，世界工人面临的风险越来越大</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/worlds-workers-increasingly-at-risk-as-climate-changes-ilo-says/articleshow/109499457.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109499457.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;全球劳动力面临着不断升级的气候风险，工人容易受到紫外线辐射和空气污染等各种危害的影响。政府需要采取紧急行动，保护工人免受气候相关疾病和死亡的影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:44:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/worlds-workers-increasingly-at-risk-as-climate-changes-ilo-says/articleshow/109499457.cms</guid></item><item><title>报告称，欧洲是变暖最快的大陆，几乎是全球平均速度的两倍</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/europe-is-the-fastest-warming-continent-at-nearly-twice-the-average-global-rate-report-says/articleshow/109499184.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109499184.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧洲面临气候变化导致的气温快速上升、健康风险和经济损失。向可再生能源过渡至关重要。尽管一些地区的气温低于平均水平，但对全球变暖后果的担忧仍然存在。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:35:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/europe-is-the-fastest-warming-continent-at-nearly-twice-the-average-global-rate-report-says/articleshow/109499184.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾东部县发生地震</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-rattled-by-earthquake-in-eastern-county/articleshow/109498951.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109498951.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;台湾气象局称，台湾东部花莲县周一发生 5.5 级地震，目前尚未收到受损情况报告。本月早些时候，花莲发生里氏7.2级地震，造成至少14人死亡，此后台湾又发生了数百次余震。台湾位于两个板块交界处，地震频发。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:28:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-rattled-by-earthquake-in-eastern-county/articleshow/109498951.cms</guid></item><item><title>在习近平的领导下，中国间谍机构认为外国威胁“无处不在”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-ministry-of-state-security-mss-xi-jiping-chinas-spy-agency/articleshow/109490898.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109490898.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;对国家安全的高度关注是习近平强调外部威胁战略的一部分，一些分析人士认为这是转移国内对其政策批评的一种策略。这种方法包括扩大中国反间谍法中间谍活动的定义，创造一个更广泛的范围，可以影响正常的商业活动并加强国内的监视。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 05:36:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-ministry-of-state-security-mss-xi-jiping-chinas-spy-agency/articleshow/109490898.cms</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚大学因反以色列抗议而取消课程</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/columbia-university-cancels-classes-amid-anti-israel-protests/articleshow/109498604.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109498604.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/columbia-university-cancels-classes-amid-anti-israel-protests/articleshow/109498604.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗总统抵达伊斯兰堡开始为期三天的访问后与巴基斯坦总理举行会谈</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-president-holds-talks-with-pakistani-premier-after-arrival-in-islamabad-for-a-3-day-visit/articleshow/109498164.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109498164.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:06:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-president-holds-talks-with-pakistani-premier-after-arrival-in-islamabad-for-a-3-day-visit/articleshow/109498164.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列 Netzah Yehuda 营被指控什么？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/what-is-the-israeli-netzah-yehuda-battalion-accused-of/articleshow/109497729.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109497729.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据以色列媒体报道，美国将对以色列内扎·耶胡达营实施制裁，原因是其对待约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的方式。以色列政府创建该营作为这些群体在军队服役的途径，允许他们维持宗教习俗，例如给他们祈祷和学习的时间，并限制他们与女兵的互动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 08:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/what-is-the-israeli-netzah-yehuda-battalion-accused-of/articleshow/109497729.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事情报局长因未能阻止 10 月 7 日袭击事件而辞职</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-military-intelligence-chief-resigns-over-failure-to-prevent-october-7-attack/articleshow/109495607.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109495607.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿哈龙·哈利瓦少将的辞职为以色列最高安全官员预计将因哈马斯的袭击造成更大影响奠定了基础，当时武装分子炸毁了以色列的边境防御工事，在数小时内毫无抵抗地横冲直撞地闯入以色列社区，造成 1,200 人死亡，其中大多数是平民，并劫持了大约 250 名人质进入加沙。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:53:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-military-intelligence-chief-resigns-over-failure-to-prevent-october-7-attack/articleshow/109495607.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>